Morceli Improves World 1,500-meter Race Record 
Noureddine Morceli of Algeria improved his own world 1,500-meter record
of 3 minutes 28.86 seconds Wednesday at the Nikaia Grand Prix track
meet in Nice, France.
Morceli's new result is 3 minutes 27.37 seconds, 1.49 seconds faster
than the old record set by Morceli in Italy in September 1992.
